{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 83379, "create_time": 1650608724, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "马克思是庸俗哲学吗", "timestamp": 1650608724}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 83384, "create_time": 1650608976, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "高中和大学教导的是马克思主义哲学吗", "timestamp": 1650608976}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 83388, "create_time": 1650609121, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "马克思不是庸俗哲学，庸俗马克思主义是一个名称，用来指代高中和大学教导的受到篡改的马克思主义哲学", "timestamp": 1650609121}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 83390, "create_time": 1650609265, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "马克思哲学是黑格尔之后的一种发展。\n在中国，关于马克思哲学，官僚们只懂得一句话，审时度势，揣摩上意。唯物辩证法变成了庸俗和稀泥", "timestamp": 1650609265}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 83392, "create_time": 1650609304, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "哲学是专业内容并不是通俗内容。就像牛顿力学电磁学是通俗内容而量子场论标准模型是专业内容", "timestamp": 1650609304}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 83396, "create_time": 1650609582, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "马克思自己领导工人运动也没让工人去读懂他的哲学也没说工人们是庸俗马克思主义。", "timestamp": 1650609582}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 83422, "create_time": 1650611791, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "上学期马原有幸自己学习了唯心主义，觉得高中大学学的真的不全面", "timestamp": 1650611791}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 83423, "create_time": 1650611815, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 当代科学哲学是专业内容没错，但正如物理学、数学、历史学中亦含有通俗内容，哲学中也有通俗内容。这部分内容可以用来训练学生的批判性思维。", "timestamp": 1650611815}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 83856, "create_time": 1650638496, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "你说的这种书，是不是叫哲学史", "timestamp": 1650638496}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 83858, "create_time": 1650638529, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "马克思哲学在哲学史里总有一章的", "timestamp": 1650638529}], "create_time": 1650607617, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1650638529, "likenum": 5, "n_attentions": 5, "n_comments": 10, "pid": 30361, "poll": null, "reply": 10, "text": "想编制一套哲学课本，教育真正的哲学，关于本体论、认识论、逻辑学和伦理学的哲学，无论高中还是大学都应该教导真正的哲学，而不是看似粗制滥造实则处心积虑的庸俗马克思主义哲学。可惜我目前还没有这个能力，也没有合适的社会环境。", "timestamp": 1650607617}}